page.title: 01SUMMARY NOMANSLAND AREA
page.content: We have attempted over the following pages to give an account of part of village life in Nomansland in the year 1985.Our subject headings are the following. P.3 P.17 A History Of Nomansland-Victoria/ Samantha. P.4 Nomansland 1985-Louise/Nicholette. P.6 Extract from the Log books of Nomansland School 1939-1945-Benjamin/ Oliver. P.8 A day in the life of 9/10 year old girl-Rebecca/Isobel. P.10 A day in the life of 10/11 year old boy-Timothy/Leon. P.12 Technology in 1985-Edward/Paul. P.14 A section of stories from the Newspapers 1985-Joanna/Alasdair. P.16 A typicial shopping list in 1985-Sarah/Abigail. P.18 A selection of T.V programmes 1985-Barry/Alec.
